{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/berbagi-kebaikan-untuksemua-lewat-komik/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Berbagi Kebaikan #UntukSemua Lewat Komik","content":"<p>Ramadan telah tiba! Saatnya berbagi kebaikan #untuksemua. Tapi, kebaikan nggak harus dilakukan dalam bentuk materi aja, lho. <a href=\"http://www.ciayo.com\">CIAYO Comics</a> mengajak para komikus untuk menyebarkan kebaikan lewat komik. Emang bisa? Bisa donk!</p>\n<p>Yuk, kalian-kalian yang pada jago gambar, tunjukkan niat baik dan semangat Ramadan dalam bentuk karya. Kalian boleh banget lho bikin komik strips dengan tema kebaikan. Kita semua ga sabar lihat komik strip kamu! Caranya? Upload di Instagram masing-masing, mention @ciayocom dan pakai hashtag #untuksemua. Jangan lupa ajak rekan-rekan komikus lainnya untuk ikutan, ya!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_4981\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4981\" data-attachment-id=\"4981\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagi-kebaikan-untuksemua-lewat-komik/attachment/ig-2-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IG-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,608\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"IG-2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IG-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IG-2.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-4981 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IG-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"608\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-4981\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">1 komik strip = 1 kebaikan (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<div></div>\n<div>Serunya, semua karya komik strip yang terkumpul, akan di-<em>share</em> di <a href=\"http://www.blog.ciayo.com\">CIAYO Blog</a>, fanpage <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ciayocom/\">facebook CIAYO Comics</a> dan <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/ciayocom/\">Instagram CIAYO Comics</a>.  Setiap karya komik yang menyertakan <em>mention</em> @ciayocom dan <em>hashtag</em> #ciayocomics dan akan di-<em>print</em> dan ditempel di paket buka puasa yang dibagikan ke anak-anak jalanan pada hari Selasa tanggal 20 Juni 2017. Periode berbagi kebaikan ini terhitung dimulai 1-20 Juni 2017.</div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_5050\" style=\"width: 1090px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-5050\" data-attachment-id=\"5050\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/berbagi-kebaikan-untuksemua-lewat-komik/attachment/ig-3-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IG-3-1.png\" data-orig-size=\"1080,1080\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"IG 3\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IG-3-1.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IG-3-1.png\" class=\"wp-image-5050 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/IG-3-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-5050\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Mekanisme (Sumber: CIAYO Comics)</p></div></p>\n<p>Template komik, dapat di-<em>download</em> <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B7qWuzviESXzWVJsTjFqd1Frek0/view?usp=sharing\">di sini</a>. Yuk, berbagi kebaikan #untuksemua bareng <a href=\"http://www.ciayo.com\">CIAYO Comics</a>!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"57a8c63f-7663-50f7-be14-8c2777911d3d"}}}